Sure! Here's a travel plan for your group of 3 from Myrtle Beach to Massachusetts, visiting 2 cities (Boston and Martha's Vineyard) over five days, from March 12th to March 16th, 2022. The total cost of this trip is $3,785.

Day 1: Myrtle Beach to Boston (March 12, 2022)
- Flight from Myrtle Beach to Boston on 2022-03-12 (Flight Number F3613545, Price $260 per person, Duration 1 hour 50 minutes, Departure Time 18:13, Arrival Time 20:03)
- Total cost for flights: $780

Accommodation in Boston (March 12 - March 14, 2022)
- Entire home/apt in Midtown East, Boston (No children under 10 & No smoking, Price $450 per night, Rating 4.5, Size 1 bedroom, Amenities: Wifi, Kitchen, Heating, TV)
- Total cost for accommodation: $900

Day 2: Exploring Boston (March 13, 2022)
- Rent a car in Boston for one day to explore the city (Price $75, Duration 24 hours)
- Visit Faneuil Hall Marketplace for lunch and try some American cuisine at Quincy Market
- Visit the New England Aquarium and enjoy the view from the Skywalk Observatory
- For dinner, try Indian cuisine at the famous restaurant, India Quality Cuisine
- Total cost for car rental and activities: $150

Day 3: Boston to Martha's Vineyard (March 14, 2022)
- Self-driving from Boston to Woods Hole, Massachusetts (Duration 2 hours 34 mins, Distance 146 km, Cost $7)
- Ferry from Woods Hole to Martha's Vineyard (Price $18 per person, Duration 45 minutes)
- Total cost for transportation: $53

Accommodation in Martha's Vineyard (March 14 - March 16, 2022)
- Entire home/apt in Edgartown, Martha's Vineyard (No children under 10 & No smoking, Price $450 per night, Rating 4.8, Size 3 bedrooms, Amenities: Wifi, Kitchen, Heating, TV)
- Total cost for accommodation: $900

Day 4: Exploring Martha's Vineyard (March 15, 2022)
- Rent a car in Martha's Vineyard for one day to explore the island (Price $75, Duration 24 hours)
- Visit the Aquinnah Cliffs and the lighthouse for breathtaking views
- For lunch, try Mexican cuisine at La Choza in Oak Bluffs
- Visit the Martha's Vineyard Gourmet Cafe & Bakery for some delicious Mediterranean food
- Total cost for car rental and activities: $150

Day 5: Martha's Vineyard to Myrtle Beach (March 16, 2022)
- Ferry from Martha's Vineyard to Woods Hole (Price $18 per person, Duration 45 minutes)
- Self-driving from Woods Hole to Boston (Duration 2 hours 34 mins, Distance 146 km, Cost $7)
- Flight from Boston to Myrtle Beach on 2022-03-16 (Flight Number TBD, Price $250 per person, Duration TBD, Departure Time TBD, Arrival Time TBD)
- Total cost for transportation: $538

Total Cost of the Trip: $3,785
